verbose_text: Led by ICMART in partnership with ASRM, ESHRE, IFFS, MOD, AFS, GIERAF, ASPIRE, MEFS, REDLARA and FIGO, consensus agreement was reached by a global representation of multi-disciplinary experts and patient representatives on 283 terms and definitions which are listed in alphabetical order.
